{"tid":1459622,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"遊客都唔走，一齊屌共狗，現場一手料！","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:26:08.000Z","uid":288370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14691e6ea2a30fcc7ee7d18d9f2c9c3792d67003","tid":1459622,"uid":288370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要留！要守！要接力！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">國際機場 通宵運作 </span></strong><br />\n我哋坐喺度 邊個犯法？<br />\n有人清場就有全世界睇住 <br />\n佢拉一個就即係話俾全球旅客知：<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">原來喺國際機場行企瞓係犯法嘅。</span><br />\n<br />\n收到任何警車防暴消息都諗一諗，結果只有一個：<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">五大訴求未達到</span>，永遠都係警黑正苦嘅錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國際社會會制裁 黑警會有報應 暴權會閪尻冧</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警還眼 暴權還命</strong></span><br />\n眼啊？命啊？我哋喺機場等你還！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxKRgLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxKRgLR.jpg&h=f653330d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日話留得青山在嘅<span style=\"color: green;\">明日戰士</span>們<br />\n我等緊你哋返嚟啊！<br />\n聽朝我哋搭頭班車返屋企衝涼<br />\n聽朝你哋頭班機入嚟飲個早茶<br />\n今日情緒病告假，聽日要覆診續假，後日又會復發喎⋯<br />\n正苦再唔出嚟對症下藥，後遺症手尾長啊⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>話罷就罷 不罷不休 持續咁罷 接力去罷</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015835_e4897445020a251037eb44804f80ccd7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015835_e4897445020a251037eb44804f80ccd7.jpeg&h=a6cb7d26&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015836_bc541ac20754111de24ca91116926766.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015836_bc541ac20754111de24ca91116926766.jpeg&h=b6587e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015837_cfbd939f7b262d6ed4b42405eb9bb5e3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015837_cfbd939f7b262d6ed4b42405eb9bb5e3.jpeg&h=f0953262&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015839_f286e406de249e3f0f2d3dbf5ce80587.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015839_f286e406de249e3f0f2d3dbf5ce80587.jpeg&h=dc0c1fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/13/015840_43b458b16c046d1336d2b9ba102539c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2F015840_43b458b16c046d1336d2b9ba102539c4.png&h=a82c02d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oqALAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oqALAZ.jpg&h=6b440aa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkPqonG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkPqonG.jpg&h=5c590cba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rkheun.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rkheun.jpg&h=ba41d73f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd8482ae7ea8cfb9b46dfe765d129c3cbb63ad52","tid":1459622,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:41:28.000Z","msg":"罷啦罷罷罷"},{"pid":"2bc73616ad3fbe147b16d1eebf703a8392b30a96","tid":1459622,"uid":263443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:48:33.000Z","msg":"入去一齊討論機場作戰戰術呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n《和你飛 無限之戰》戰術討論整理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459625\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459625</a>"},{"pid":"f2356e73e36d6668ad76adabca537d6807faaebd","tid":1459622,"uid":300554,"like":4,"di